---
// Instrucciones de la Calculadora Numerológica
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white relative">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    
    <!-- Header de Instrucciones -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#e6b866]"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.376 3.622a1 1 0 0 1 3.002 3.002L7.368 18.635a2 2 0 0 1-.855.506l-2.872.838a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.838-2.872a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.854z"/></svg>
        Instrucciones importantes
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 font-sans text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Para que el cálculo numerológico sea exacto según el sistema cabalístico, es <strong class="font-medium text-slate-800">fundamental</strong> que los datos que ingreses sean completos y fieles a tu identidad personal.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de Instrucciones -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Card 1: Nombre -->
      <div class="group bg-[#FCFBF9] p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-[#B11252] shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(177,18,82,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-[#B11252] group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-800">Nombre completo</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Introduce tu nombre tal como aparece en tu acta o certificado del Registro Civil, sin abreviaciones ni apodos.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 font-sans space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Correcto:</span> María de los Dolores
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Incorrecto:</span> Mariló o M. Dolores
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Apellidos -->
      <div class="group bg-[#FCFBF9] p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-[#e6b866] shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(230,184,102,0.12)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-[#e6b866] group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-800">Apellidos compuestos</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Si tienes un apellido compuesto (por ejemplo, <span class="font-medium text-slate-700 italic">Fernández de Córdoba</span>), introdúcelo completo en una sola casilla.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed">
          El sistema lo considerará inteligentemente como un único bloque energético.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Fecha -->
      <div class="group bg-[#FCFBF9] p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-slate-700 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/><path d="M8 14h.01"/><path d="M12 14h.01"/><path d="M16 14h.01"/><path d="M8 18h.01"/><path d="M12 18h.01"/><path d="M16 18h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-800">Fecha de nacimiento</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Utiliza tu fecha <strong class="font-medium text-slate-700">real</strong> de nacimiento, incluso si no coincide con la que figura en el Registro Civil.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed">
          La fecha astronómica de tu encarnación es la clave fundamental para el cálculo preciso de tus números.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Idioma -->
      <div class="group bg-[#FCFBF9] p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-emerald-600 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(5,150,105,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-emerald-600 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-800">Idioma materno</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Selecciona la lengua con la que te sientes más cómodo hablando. Si eres bilingüe, elige aquella con la que te identificas más íntimamente.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
          "Y si tienes dudas, elige la lengua con la que te comunicabas con tu madre en la infancia."
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
